+# Reactive Spreadsheet Engine Design
+
+## Architecture
+
+Multi-file structure in `src/`:
+
+- `index.ts` — `Spreadsheet` class (public API)
+- `parser.ts` — Recursive descent formula parser producing an AST
+- `evaluator.ts` — AST evaluator that resolves cell refs and computes values
+- `types.ts` — Shared types (AST nodes, cell value types)
+
+## Key Decisions
+
+1. **Hand-written recursive descent parser** for formulas. Grammar is simple (arithmetic, comparisons, function calls, cell refs, ranges).
+2. **Eager recomputation** — on `set()`, immediately recompute all transitive dependents using topological sort order.
+3. **Dependency graph** — adjacency list. Each cell tracks what it depends on (`dependencies`) and what depends on it (`dependents`). Updated when formulas change.
+4. **Circular reference detection** — DFS-based cycle detection before committing a formula. Throw error and reject the `set()` call if cycle found.
+5. **Cell references** — parse column letters to 0-based index (A=0, Z=25, AA=26, etc.) and row number to 0-based index.
+
+## Formula Grammar
+
+```
+expression  = comparison
+comparison  = addition (( '>' | '<' | '>=' | '<=' | '=' | '<>' ) addition)?
+addition    = multiplication (( '+' | '-' ) multiplication)*
+multiplication = unary (( '*' | '/' ) unary)*
+unary       = '-' unary | primary
+primary     = NUMBER | STRING | BOOLEAN | CELL_REF | FUNCTION_CALL | '(' expression ')'
+FUNCTION_CALL = IDENTIFIER '(' arglist ')'
+arglist     = (expression | range) (',' (expression | range))*
+range       = CELL_REF ':' CELL_REF
+```
+
+## Reactive Update Algorithm
+
+1. On `set(cell, value)`:
+   - Parse formula if value starts with `=`
+   - Extract new dependencies from AST
+   - Check for cycles (DFS from dependents back to cell)
+   - Update dependency/dependent maps
+   - Evaluate cell
+   - Topologically sort all transitive dependents
+   - Re-evaluate each in order
+
+## Testing Strategy
+
+- Unit tests for cell reference parsing
+- Unit tests for formula parser
+- Unit tests for evaluator
+- Integration tests for Spreadsheet class (set/get, reactive updates, circular refs, functions, ranges)
